title: TAVIK Swimwear + AGOGO Collaboration | Behind the Scenes Vid
description:
Shop the TAVIK X AGOGO collection here - http://shop.tavik.com/tavik-x-agogo/t...

This is a behind-the-scenes interview with Jen (Agogo) Humphrey, top fashion blogger and model, discussing the inspiration behind her collaboration line with TAVIK® Swimwear, a California-based lifestyle brand. TAVIK and Jen partnered to create a timeless yet sexy, rock n' roll inspired swimwear collection. Each piece in the TAVIK X AGOGO collection has been meticulously designed by both parties to perfectly translate your late night antics into poolside fun.
